{"tid":1038112,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"視光師冀做基層醫療　眼科醫生反對：應由醫生負責","createTime":"2019-02-26T12:16:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T03:16:10.000Z","uid":136252,"like":7,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"729edf8c8b8b2270db7b32a76eacb1a66c1ea3a7","tid":1038112,"uid":136252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T12:16:32.000Z","msg":"本港面臨人口老化，政府近年大力推動基層醫療，務求在社區層面處理穩定個案、減輕公立醫院的壓力，首間位於葵青的地區康健中心預料在今年第三季提供服務，相關招標結果料快將公布。<br />\n<br />\n公營眼科專科門診的輪候時間一直位列榜首，新症最長需輪候逾3年。香港眼科視光師學會代表接受訪問時認為，大部份長者的眼部疾病只需定期監察，註冊視光師可在基層醫療擔當分流的角色，又認為視光師應有轉介病人到公立醫院求診的權力。<br />\n<br />\n但有眼科醫生則認為，基層醫療應由受過醫學訓練的家庭醫生診斷病情後再作轉介，不應鼓勵病人自行斷定身體狀況。"},{"pid":"75f3812cf905bdc9435116fe9eb1471b8d15b74f","tid":1038112,"uid":136252,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T12:17:12.000Z","msg":"基層醫療是近年政府在講述醫療政策時經常提及的方向，若由在地區的康健中心處理較穩定的病人個案，公立醫院的壓力相對可以減輕。有註冊視光師提出，視光師在基層醫療層面亦幫得上忙。"},{"pid":"94a8f2c4ac9a2bc5eb8d68e1f35f9c5534645f51","tid":1038112,"uid":136252,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T12:17:35.000Z","msg":"視光師學會：有能力診斷長者是否受患白內障<br />\n<br />\n現時本港的視光師分為四類，第一部份註冊視光師，是指完成香港理工大學視光學理學士課程的人，這批視光師與其餘三類視光師的分別在於沒有執業限制，亦可以使用核准的藥物，包括局部麻醉藥、擴瞳藥及睫狀肌麻痺劑。<br />\n<br />\n香港眼科視光師學會會長羅桂媚受訪時指，第一部份註冊的視光師受過專業訓練，亦有相當的知識水平，可為病人提供全面的眼睛健康檢查，包括驗視網膜是否完整、有無斜視、色弱等問題，就眼睛疾病作診斷及跟進，與舊日的「驗光師」只負責驗眼睛度數不同。若有長者只知自己「眼矇」，視光師亦有能力診斷長者是否受白內障或「糖尿上眼」等病所困。"},{"pid":"03f1c1a58540ffab337fc0b61cf40900b449c557","tid":1038112,"uid":136252,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T12:17:58.000Z","msg":"眼科醫生：視光師無能力做適當轉介<br />\n<br />\n香港眼科醫學院院長黎少明受訪時反駁有關建議，他強調基層醫療的目的是由受過醫學訓練的醫生為病人分流，診斷出病人的各種毛病，再按疾病的嚴重性排優次，並轉介病人至不同專科跟進治療。他認為視光師是非常專門的範疇，若病人先向視光師求診，變相鼓勵病人自行決定判斷身體有哪種毛病急需處理，在基層醫療而言是本末倒置。<br />\n<br />\n黎少明續指，若長者有眼部退化問題，意味其身體其他器官亦會有退化問題，只注重眼睛檢查或會忽略其他疾病。他舉例，即使視光師可檢查到糖尿病引發的眼水腫，但心臟、腎、腦部等亦同受影響，視光師無相關知識及能力作適當轉介。他又提到，由於視光師不能向病人處方藥物，即使獲得轉介權，遇到未能處理的病人個案亦只能直接轉介至公立醫院醫生，變相增加公營醫療負擔。<br />\n<br />\n黎認為，最理想的做法是由醫生做分流，若有合適個案便交視光師跟進，務求讓病人得到全面的治療。"},{"pid":"ca26ac4d5a4f37f1f123932b3fe8f6aec92687a7","tid":1038112,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T12:40:34.000Z","msg":"公營眼科專科門診的輪候時間一直位列榜首，新症最長需輪候逾3年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。"},{"pid":"35e0996335bac66e553a20e11bea7cb467d7626b","tid":1038112,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T12:41:45.000Z","msg":"有冇人知邊區輪候時間最短<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"591dd826e2f35cbc53e66d6f1c29f83aada94e21","tid":1038112,"uid":56698,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T12:55:05.000Z","msg":"有都話你冇啦 私家個名無啦啦畀你分大咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cec5136db2b73f09711bb318cf07d488a8388a9a","tid":1038112,"uid":215141,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T13:07:07.000Z","msg":"&quot;即使獲得轉介權，遇到未能處理的病人個案亦只能直接轉介至公立醫院醫生，變相增加公營醫療負擔&quot;<br />\n就算冇轉介，病人有事都會去公立醫院啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"818239f12fa0871251f74bdbc723f7b1315b2c10","tid":1038112,"uid":89514,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T14:11:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7b3bea825f1f6f5e08894de8b8d68db9bdacd167","tid":1038112,"uid":128761,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T15:27:58.000Z","msg":"香港醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當外國護士都可以做診斷時<br />\n香港既專職醫療人員只可以做狗"},{"pid":"10cc614b813d82bcc8768a26dafb844633f9a945","tid":1038112,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T16:27:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6026450d68579d7e832a1319052b8ee71ed51ccd","tid":1038112,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T16:30:08.000Z","msg":"惡性循環黎<br />\n冇得變<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eec0cfe121bfdf86d2dd66b2d75685e38cd4370","tid":1038112,"uid":196329,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T16:36:06.000Z","msg":"大家唔好信呢d新聞<br />\n全部都係用黎攻擊香港醫生，以便引入大陸醫生<br />\n香港絕對冇醫學霸權，所有醫生都係以病人利益行先"},{"pid":"34c8f9f0ca5fa470868196981a2e73db991e03c3","tid":1038112,"uid":61882,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-26T16:44:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>大家唔好信呢d新聞<br />\n全部都係用黎攻擊香港醫生，以便引入大陸醫生<br />\n香港絕對冇醫學霸權，所有醫生都係以<del>病人</del>牟取利益行先</blockquote>"},{"pid":"1c93e334f2e924354ba992172bf702d19f7f5b04","tid":1038112,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T01:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0a792e7155e7f6f1bf4a6f87bed6db259e9c6d7","tid":1038112,"uid":61271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T02:32:51.000Z","msg":"大家都係想分醫療券個餅姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70818de69aac0a4f0ef72952e1e5e442041ea16d","tid":1038112,"uid":18251,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T02:58:47.000Z","msg":"視光師想當自己喺眼科醫生？<br />\n重使咩咁辛苦讀書。"},{"pid":"6b2fdb562b366d66a20d29e8a64aaecdd9a3e500","tid":1038112,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"70818de69aac0a4f0ef72952e1e5e442041ea16d","tid":1038112,"uid":18251,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T02:58:47.000Z","msg":"視光師想當自己喺眼科醫生？<br />\n重使咩咁辛苦讀書。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T03:03:10.000Z","msg":"其實睇係咪白內障之類，洗撚搵眼科醫生分流<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4320d2cb12636273f2413f642823afd7a3bfd1a7","tid":1038112,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T03:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vAyiJKC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvAyiJKC.png&h=baa2d07e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然事實係輪候得耐<br />\n<br />\n醫療券既利益已經向視光師傾鈄<br />\n而且醫生專業怎樣外判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ced12cda6d9cc761fafb11b4f21f6507def352a0","tid":1038112,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4320d2cb12636273f2413f642823afd7a3bfd1a7","tid":1038112,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T03:05:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vAyiJKC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvAyiJKC.png&h=baa2d07e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然事實係輪候得耐<br />\n<br />\n醫療券既利益已經向視光師傾鈄<br />\n而且醫生專業怎樣外判<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T03:14:51.000Z","msg":"咩 app <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8462ee4b7ee7f2973d26d1d5b12cef6dfb22d8c3","tid":1038112,"uid":51937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70818de69aac0a4f0ef72952e1e5e442041ea16d","tid":1038112,"uid":18251,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T02:58:47.000Z","msg":"視光師想當自己喺眼科醫生？<br />\n重使咩咁辛苦讀書。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T03:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}